            "title": "Molecular phylogenetics of slit‐faced bats (Chiroptera: Nycteridae) reveal deeply divergent African lineages",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Terrence C.",
                    "lastName": "Demos"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
