            "title": "MATCHING MORPHOLOGY AND DIET IN THE DISC-WINGED BAT THYROPTERA TRICOLOR (CHIROPTERA)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Dina K. N.",
